RelatedSentence: WASHINGTON , May 19 , 2014 - The Defense Department will ship 26 tons of humanitarian relief to the people of Bosnia and Herzegovina as early as tomorrow following severe flooding in the Balkans , Pentagon spokesman Army Col. Steve Warren told reporters today .
